{
  "chunk_id": 2,
  "start_offset": 2390.0,
  "segments": [
    {
      "idx": 0,
      "start": 2390.0,
      "end": 2391.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "几乎都是在山東青島,因為青島是北方最大的這個海產品以及各種各樣農產品",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 1,
      "start": 2391.0,
      "end": 2392.8,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "甚至一些工業品的進口港嗎?",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 2,
      "start": 2393.0,
      "end": 2394.9,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "青島和黃島嘛,如果有當地朋友大家都知道。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 3,
      "start": 2395.0,
      "end": 2397.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "很多的工業品、農產品其實都是在青島入的港。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 4,
      "start": 2397.0,
      "end": 2400.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "所以入港之後就地就找一個工廠了,它其實就很大程度能夠帶動當地的就業了。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 5,
      "start": 2400.4,
      "end": 2400.8,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "謝謝。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.99,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 6,
      "start": 2401.4,
      "end": 2403.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "然後接下來給大家來了一個翡翠生蝦人。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 7,
      "start": 2403.4,
      "end": 2409.1,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "這個裡頭之前我們賣的蝦人裡頭有比較多的那個冰的包衣,然後有的朋友反應那個鹹蝦人小,鹹那個包衣有點多。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 8,
      "start": 2409.1,
      "end": 2412.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "那我們就給大家找了這個,當然你你的這個蝦人含量多少不一樣,它的價格其實也就不一樣了。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 9,
      "start": 2412.0,
      "end": 2413.8,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "所以如果你想吃這個的話,你可以試一試。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 10,
      "start": 2414.0,
      "end": 2416.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "它的配料表也分乾淨,來給大家展示一下,導演給個進景,你看它的配料表。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 11,
      "start": 2416.2,
      "end": 2420.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "The only ingredients are shrimp and water, nothing else, okay?就這兩個東西,蝦人和水。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 12,
      "start": 2420.2,
      "end": 2424.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "家裡真正做飯的人就知道這個挑蝦線,挑蝦線去去蝦頭那些是多麼的麻煩。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 13,
      "start": 2424.4,
      "end": 2428.9,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "早上起來,比如說你自己要健康早餐,對吧,拿雞蛋和這個一炒,迅速就好了。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 14,
      "start": 2429.0,
      "end": 2432.9,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "或者家裡有孩子要上學,著急都要走了,你這個早餐還沒有做好,其實就很麻煩。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 15,
      "start": 2433.0,
      "end": 2436.9,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "那這個時候就拿著這個蝦人和雞蛋炒一下,既方便又營養,好嗎?",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 16,
      "start": 2437.0,
      "end": 2438.4,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "有朋友說要楊梅汁,導演有的話給大家談一下。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 17,
      "start": 2438.6,
      "end": 2439.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "OK。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.99,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 18,
      "start": 2439.3,
      "end": 2440.0,
      "speaker": "other",
      "text": "楊梅汁,楊梅汁沒有。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 19,
      "start": 2440.3,
      "end": 2440.6,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "沒了。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.99,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 20,
      "start": 2441.0,
      "end": 2441.7,
      "speaker": "other",
      "text": "楊梅汁也沒有了。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 21,
      "start": 2442.0,
      "end": 2442.3,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "OK。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.99,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 22,
      "start": 2449.0,
      "end": 2400.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "嗯,還有朋友說要什麼?",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 23,
      "start": 2400.0,
      "end": 2400.3,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "要中國哲學史,中國哲學史那本書今天沒有對吧?",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 24,
      "start": 2400.3,
      "end": 2400.4,
      "speaker": "other",
      "text": "今天沒有。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 25,
      "start": 2400.4,
      "end": 2400.6,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "如果你想買的書,您關注我們直播間啊。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 26,
      "start": 2400.6,
      "end": 2401.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我們也會按照,當然我的觀點不一定對啊,我也時常在這裡首先自我批評做反思。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 27,
      "start": 2401.0,
      "end": 2401.4,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我會按照我之前讀書的很多的方式給大家去繼續尋找,這只是一個開始。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 28,
      "start": 2401.4,
      "end": 2401.6,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我們不可能一生只讀這幾本書。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 29,
      "start": 2401.6,
      "end": 2401.7,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "讀書讀的少,本本都是好,對吧?",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 30,
      "start": 2401.7,
      "end": 2402.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我們就這一點書是不可能想明白人生的很多問題的。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 31,
      "start": 2402.0,
      "end": 2402.5,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我們這一點點偏頗而荒謬的觀點也不可能去指導別人的人生。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 32,
      "start": 2402.5,
      "end": 2402.9,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我們這一點點所擁有的知識和智慧也很難去解決人生未來所有的問題。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 33,
      "start": 2402.9,
      "end": 2403.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "有一件事是確定的。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 34,
      "start": 2403.4,
      "end": 2403.6,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "就是就於老師所說的,你終將會離開這個世界。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 35,
      "start": 2403.6,
      "end": 2403.9,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "但不確定的是你在什麼時候以什麼方式離開這個世界。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 36,
      "start": 2404.0,
      "end": 2404.3,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "那同樣在看書這件事情是確定是,有一件事確定就是你肯定是要一直持續去閱讀的。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 37,
      "start": 2404.3,
      "end": 2404.7,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "閱讀很多時候我並不是為了直接,你讀書那我讀這書對我有什麼用?",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 38,
      "start": 2404.7,
      "end": 2404.9,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "對我工作有什麼用?能不能讓我賺錢?",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 39,
      "start": 2404.9,
      "end": 2405.1,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "你要這樣想的話,你還不如不讀了,朋友。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 40,
      "start": 2405.1,
      "end": 2405.3,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "如果你一直在這樣問我的話,那你還不如不讀了。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 41,
      "start": 2405.6,
      "end": 2405.9,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "你就繼續去糾結現實中的很多問題,你就繼續精神空虛,然後思想匱乏。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 42,
      "start": 2405.9,
      "end": 2406.2,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "就像我前幾天講的,為什麼於老師要求新東方老師讀書呢?",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 43,
      "start": 2406.2,
      "end": 2406.7,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "如果你一個老師,你自己都不讀幾本書,你精神那麼匱乏,你如何去觸碰另一個靈魂啊?",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 44,
      "start": 2407.1,
      "end": 2407.4,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "你一張嘴就讓人感覺到你沒有深度,你怎麼能夠吸引別人啊?",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 45,
      "start": 2407.7,
      "end": 2408.2,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "你都沒有辦法旁徵博引,深入淺出,微妙微笑,誰願意聽你啊?",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 46,
      "start": 2408.2,
      "end": 2408.3,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "大概就是這種意思。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 47,
      "start": 2408.4,
      "end": 2408.7,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "對不起,我今天上來賣貨其實沒有賣貨,我一直在扯扯著一些扯了很多。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 48,
      "start": 2408.7,
      "end": 2408.9,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "書也沒有賣幾本,是吧?",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 49,
      "start": 2408.9,
      "end": 2409.0,
      "speaker": "other",
      "text": "賣錢。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 50,
      "start": 2409.1,
      "end": 2409.2,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我今天賣多少本書?",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 51,
      "start": 2409.2,
      "end": 2409.4,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我剛在帶貨的時候有排名嗎?",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 52,
      "start": 2409.6,
      "end": 2409.7,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "沒有是吧?",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 53,
      "start": 2409.7,
      "end": 2409.8,
      "speaker": "other",
      "text": "帶貨榜上。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 54,
      "start": 2409.8,
      "end": 2409.9,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "一直是啊。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 55,
      "start": 2409.9,
      "end": 2410.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "那也行,那也行。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 56,
      "start": 2410.0,
      "end": 2410.4,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我特別害怕我一賣書,因為其實我在這講書只是因為個人喜歡而已,我就有時候說下來就不停,有時候就不管別人的體驗。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 57,
      "start": 2410.5,
      "end": 2410.9,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "直播間裡其實很多朋友大家想要買東西,可能我時候信息太多了,因為這有35、6萬人。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 58,
      "start": 2410.9,
      "end": 2411.1,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "剛才有40多萬人呢都。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 59,
      "start": 2411.1,
      "end": 2411.3,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我看不到有時候消息發太快了,我可能給大家回不清楚。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 60,
      "start": 2411.4,
      "end": 2411.5,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "對不起。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.99,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 61,
      "start": 2411.5,
      "end": 2411.8,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "如果您需要,您可以在右下角小黃車裡自己去看,自己去買,好不好?",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 62,
      "start": 2411.8,
      "end": 2412.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我們特別希望這成為一個超市。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 63,
      "start": 2412.0,
      "end": 2412.1,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "超市是什麼感覺?",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 64,
      "start": 2412.1,
      "end": 2412.2,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "你不僅不慢啊。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 65,
      "start": 2412.2,
      "end": 2412.7,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "你跟你的愛人,跟你的孩子推著車,對吧,甚至還把孩子放在車裡頭,親一親他的小臉蛋,摸一摸他的頭髮。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 66,
      "start": 2412.7,
      "end": 2413.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "你們不僅不慢的在超市裡逛,慢慢挑呢。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 67,
      "start": 2413.0,
      "end": 2413.1,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "你覺得呢?",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 68,
      "start": 2413.1,
      "end": 2413.4,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "那那小黃車其實就是我們這個超市的小貨架,您可以挑一挑。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 69,
      "start": 2413.4,
      "end": 2414.0,
      "speaker": "host",
      "text": "我特別不希望您到我們直播間之後,我們弄一個傳導的音樂或者那種特別逼得得逼人的這個文字,然後讓你盡快下單,恨不得趕快把你再趕出去一樣。",
      "text_normalized": "",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "chunk_id": 2
    },
    {
      "idx": 70,
      "start": 2414.0,
      "end": 2414.2,
      "speaker": "host",
